de.iabg.mode.plaf
Class ModeFilter

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.filechooser.FileFilter
      de.iabg.swing.filechooser.AbstractFilter
          de.iabg.mode.plaf.ModeFilter

public class ModeFilter
extends AbstractFilter

This implementation of FileFilter provides the supported extensions for mode files. In general, the user should create one ModeFilter object of each supported type and attach them to the JFileChooser.

Version:
September 13, 2008
Author:
Adam C. Dick, BSE
